@NODE "System" "System Requirements"
@TOC "MAIN"

 @{b}System Requirements@{ub}
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 An Amiga?

 Well, You need OS 2.0 or better to play the game. If you don't have
 a harddisk you have to wait a few second for the game to load the
 choosed background, so if you want to change the background without
 waiting, I think you have to buy a harddisk.
 To get the best view of the MagicWB icon you must have the MagicWB
 colours (MagicWB by Martin Hutterloher). I think this is all you need
 to play GSReversi painless.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Install" "GSReversi Installation/Uninstallation"
@TOC "MAIN"

 @{b}GSReversi Installtion/Uninstallation@{ub}
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 GSReversi is very simple to install and uninstall, just copy the
 files to the directory you want to have the game. But you MUST
 include all the original files in the directory (see @{"Product Facts" LINK "Product"}).
 When someday want to delete GSReversi from your disk/harddisk you
 just delete the files in the directory and then the directory.

